OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer says "hanging onto
OL,7,FTrump's latest words is not the
OL,8,Fspecial relationship in action" after
OL,9,FTrump's latest attack on the prime
OL,10,Fminister over his response to the war
OL,11,Fin Iran.
OL,13,FStarmer was asked during Prime
OL,14,FMinister's Questions if his "dithering
OL,15,Fand equivocal response" to events in
OL,16,Fthe Middle East had improved the
OL,17,Frelationship with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
