PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772647566
OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,F"American planes are operating out of
OL,7,FBritish bases. That is the special
OL,8,Frelationship in action... Hanging on
OL,9,Fto President Trump's latest words is
OL,10,Fnot the special relationship in
OL,11,Faction," the PM told the Commons.
OL,13,FHe said the crisis in the Middle East
OL,14,Frequired a "cool head" as he defended
OL,15,Fhis response to the situation and that
OL,16,Fhis priority was the safety of the
OL,17,FBritish people.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
