OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772647566
OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Oval Office on Tuesday
OL,7,Fduring a visit from the German
OL,8,FChancellor, President Trump said he is
OL,9,F"not happy" with the UK and with
OL,10,FStarmer, and that "this is not Winston
OL,11,FChurchill that we're dealing with".
OL,13,FTrump's comments referred to Starmer's
OL,14,Fdecision not to be involved in the
OL,15,Finitial US strikes on Iran, despite
OL,16,Flater deciding to allow the use of
OL,17,FBritish bases for "defensive" strikes
OL,18,Fon Iranian missile sites to protect
OL,19,Fcountries being targeted by Tehran.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]rD@SOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
