OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,FDuring PMQs, Tory leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Fasked why the RAF had not taken
OL,8,F"offensive action" to destroy Iranian
OL,9,Fmissile sites after British bases in
OL,10,FBahrain and Cyprus had been attacked.
OL,12,FStarmer replied: "The protection of UK
OL,13,Fnationals is our number one priority.
OL,14,FWe're taking action to reduce the
OL,15,Fthreat with planes in the sky in the
OL,16,Fregion intercepting incoming strikes,
OL,17,Fdeploying more capability to Cyprus,
OL,18,Fand allowing US planes to use UK bases
OL,19,Fto take out Iran's capability to
OL,20,Fstrike."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]tD@ROU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
