CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772647566
OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,F"This government will be resolute in
OL,7,Four focus, protecting British lives,
OL,8,Fbringing our people home, and
OL,9,Fsafeguarding our national interest,"
OL,10,Fthe prime minister said.
OL,12,FStarmer has sought to limit UK
OL,13,Finvolvement in the war, but decided on
OL,14,FSunday that the joint British-US Diego
OL,15,FGarcia site in the Chagos Islands and
OL,16,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire could
OL,17,Fbe used defensively by the US.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
