PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772647566
OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,FHMS Dragon, one of the Royal Navy's
OL,7,Fsix Type 45 air defence destroyers, is
OL,8,Fbeing readied to depart for the
OL,9,FMediterranean to defend Cyprus after
OL,10,FRAF Akrotiri was hit by a drone.
OL,12,FIn a statement on Monday, Starmer made
OL,13,Fclear he believed the US strikes on
OL,14,FIran were not legal, saying the UK did
OL,15,Fnot support "regime change from the
OL,16,Fskies".
OL,18,FThe PM said he would not put British
OL,19,Fmilitary lives at risk unless the
OL,20,Faction had "a proper lawful basis".
OL,26,@|D@bO]
