OL,3,CStarmer: Special relationship is not
OL,4,C'hanging onto Trump's latest words'
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Reform UK
OL,7,Fleader Nigel Farage said he was "not
OL,8,Fsurprised" Trump hit out at Starmer
OL,9,Fover Iran.
OL,11,F"To say he's no Winston Churchill is
OL,12,Fquite an understatement, really. I
OL,13,Fmean the man has dithered, he's all
OL,14,Fover the place. He's not a leader,
OL,15,Fhe's a follower," Farage told a press
OL,16,Fconference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
